CONTANTES lc_pi(12)  TYPE p DECIMALS 13 VALUE '3,1415926535898'
	DATA: ld_raio(12)    TYPE p DECIMALS 2,
				 ld_area(12)    TYPE p DECIMALS 2.


	   ld_area = ( ld_raio * ld_raio ) * lc_pi
